                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card col-12" style="width: 18rem;     background-color: #9126bd;">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center">Research Labs</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Comprehensive, grade-specific, hands-on learning! Best for families looking to
                        add
